                            <comment id="16500838" author="knoguchi" created="Mon, 4 Jun 2018 20:50:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached &lt;tt&gt;pig-5341-v01.patch&lt;/tt&gt;&#160;that fixes the off-by-one bug in determining which fields to keep. &lt;br/&gt;
Also, tagfile/tagpath was always being added to tuple even when columnpruning was setting &lt;tt&gt;mRequiredColumns&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/tt&gt; to false.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Separate from this, found &lt;tt&gt;testColumnPrune&lt;/tt&gt; wasn&apos;t really comparing the output.  Fixed that as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
